ww.nme.com/artists/the-maccabees">马卡比乐队</a>还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-maccabees-on-adele-supporting-them-at-pub-in-battersea-for-200-people-pre-covid-3807941">回忆起她在新冠疫情爆发之前在伦敦举行的一场演出中支持他们的经历</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-embraces-meryl-streep-at-vegas-show-while-dressed-as-her-character-from-death-becomes-her-3809083">阿黛尔 (Adele) 在维加斯秀场拥抱梅丽尔·斯特里普 (Meryl Streep)，同时打扮成她在《死亡成为她》中的角色，</a>这一帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
