res-his-thoughts-on-taylor-swift-and-eminem-endorsing-kamala-harris-3807296" target="_blank" rel="noopener">摇滚小子（Kid Rock）</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/kelsey-grammer-banned-from-talking-about-trump-support-in-interviews-reporter-claims-3553743" target="_blank" rel="noopener">凯尔西·格拉默（Kelsey Grammer）</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-makes-a-brief-appearance-at-donald-trump-supporters-rally-in-beverly-hills-3784869" target="_blank" rel="noopener">坎耶·维斯特（Kanye West）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/hulk-hogan-asks-crowd-if-they-want-him-to-body-slam-kamala-harris-3786054">绿巨人霍根（Hulk Hogan）</a> 。</p></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/donald-trump-disappointed-in-julia-roberts-for-narrating-kamala-harris-ad-3809057">唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对朱莉娅·罗伯茨 (Julia Roberts) 为卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 广告做旁白而“失望”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
